11. Employer ECR Challenge

Target stakeholders: Employers, payroll vendors, HR teams
Game format: Spreadsheet/file validation game

The player receives a simulated monthly payroll file and must prepare a correct ECR.

They must catch errors such as:

Wrong UAN
Missing Aadhaar/KYC
Incorrect basic wage
Wrong contribution calculation
Excluded employee wrongly included
Eligible employee wrongly excluded
Date of joining/date of exit mismatch

Learning outcomes:

Practical employer training for reducing ECR errors.

Gamification:

Monthly compliance streak, error-free filing badge, payroll accuracy score.
